📋 STEP-BY-STEP SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

STEP 1: GitHub Repository Setup
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
✓ Create a new GitHub repository (or use existing one)
✓ Make sure repository is PUBLIC
✓ Upload these 4 files:
   1. app.py
   2. requirements.txt
   3. packages.txt
   4. decoder_power_delay_area_dataset.csv


STEP 2: Edit app.py (IMPORTANT!)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Open app.py and find line ~65 (around the load_decoder_data function)

FIND THIS LINE:
url = "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/YOUR_USERNAME/YOUR_REPO/main/decoder_power_delay_area_dataset.csv"

REPLACE WITH YOUR DETAILS:
url = "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/[YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME]/[YOUR_REPO_NAME]/main/decoder_power_delay_area_dataset.csv"

EXAMPLE:
If your GitHub username is: student123
And your repo name is: power-decoder-project

Then change to:
url = "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/student123/power-decoder-project/main/decoder_power_delay_area_dataset.csv"


STEP 3: Deploy on Streamlit Cloud (FREE!)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1. Go to: https://streamlit.io/cloud
2. Click "Sign in" with GitHub
3. Click "New app" button
4. Select:
   - Repository: [Your repo name]
   - Branch: main
   - Main file path: app.py
5. Click "Deploy"!
6. Wait 2-3 minutes for deployment
7. Done! Share the link with your team 🎉


STEP 4: Local Testing (Optional)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
If you want to test locally first:

# Install Python packages
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run the app
streamlit run app.py

# Open browser at: http://localhost:8501


📊 VERIFY YOUR DATASET
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
Your CSV file MUST have exactly these 13 columns:

1. decoder_size
2. tech_node
3. supply_voltage
4. threshold_voltage
5. transistor_width
6. load_capacitance
7. pg_efficiency
8. switching_activity
9. leakage_factor
10. temperature
11. power (target)
12. delay (target)
13. area (target)


🎯 TROUBLESHOOTING
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
Problem: "Error loading dataset"
Solution: Check GitHub URL is correct and repo is PUBLIC

Problem: "Missing columns in dataset"
Solution: Verify CSV has all 13 required columns

Problem: "Module not found"
Solution: Make sure requirements.txt is uploaded

Problem: App loads but no data
Solution: Check CSV file is named exactly: decoder_power_delay_area_dataset.csv


